def calculate_length_after_operations(n: int, m: int) -> int:
    mod = 10 ** 9 - 7
    N = 200000 + 10
    dp = [1] * N
    for i in range(10, N):
        dp[i] = (dp[i - 9] + dp[i - 10]) % mod
    ans = 0
    while n:
        i = n % 10
        n //= 10
        ans = (ans + dp[i + m]) % mod
    return ans
